{
  "_authoring_notes": [
    "Phase 4a-hub Section 3 — Specialty memberships 2x3 grid. REVISED 2026-04-28 EOD (final) per Jonathan's foundation-strip-below direction.",
    "Alliance was briefly placed at the top of this grid spanning 3 cols, but was MOVED to its own foundation strip BELOW the grid (Section 04). Hierarchy is now literal: 6 specialty tiles are the standing structures (top billing); Alliance is the foundation underneath.",
    "PPEF copy: 'Membership organization for national property preservation companies. Servicers and GSEs participate as institutional partners.' (Corrected from prior 'national standards body' — PPEF is a member org, not a standards body.)",
    "Specialty tile order: Row 1 = FORCE / Legal League / NMSA, Row 2 = MSEA / PPEF / AMDC.",
    "Per prior locked decisions:",
    "  - NO pricing, NO status badges. Implicit framing: 'apply for any membership'.",
    "  - Community subtitle on each specialty card (FORCE = Real Estate Professionals, etc.).",
    "  - Two buttons (Community ← / → Member Portal) on 5 cards. AMDC single button (Member Portal only — cross-community).",
    "Community button targets:",
    "  FORCE → /communities/real-estate-professionals/ (live)",
    "  Legal League / NMSA / MSEA / PPEF → /communities/ (stub, until Phase 4b builds out individual community pages)"
  ],
